            <p class="ds-c-usa-banner__media-body"><strong>Official websites use .gov</strong><br>
              A <strong>.gov</strong> website belongs to an official government organization in the United States.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="ds-c-usa-banner__guidance">
            <svg aria-hidden="true" class="ds-c-usa-banner__icon" viewBox="0 0 54 54" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M34.72 34.84a1.29 1.29 0 0 1-1.29 1.29H20.57a1.29 1.29 0 0 1-1.29-1.29v-7.72a1.29 1.29 0 0 1 1.29-1.29H21v-2.57a6 6 0 0 1 12 0v2.57h.43a1.29 1.29 0 0 1 1.29 1.29v7.72zm-4.29-9v-2.58a3.43 3.43 0 0 0-6.86 0v2.57h6.86z" fill="#719f2a"></path>
              <circle cx="27" cy="27.12" fill="none" r="26" stroke="#538200" stroke-miterlimit="10"></circle>
