            <p class="ds-c-usa-banner__media-body"><strong>Secure .gov websites use HTTPS</strong><br>
              A <strong>lock</strong> ( <svg class="ds-c-usa-banner__lock-image" role="img" viewBox="0 0 52 64" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
